"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"**Don't rely on centralised platforms with your distribution. Instead, use them to grow your own channel.**\\n\\nDistribution is an important form of leverage. When you have distribution, you own a channel to get any product or service you offer directly to your followers. Distribution channels can have different forms - this depends on what you're good at and on the type of brand you have.\\n\\nIf you want to create a distribution channel, it's important to get good at one (or more) of these:\\n\\n* Writing\\n* Speaking\\n* Graphical design\\n* Photography\\n* Filming/editing\\n* Animation\\n\\nAn important factor to take into account is to have a decentralised platform to publish your content. You don't want to depend entirely on social media or other centralised media. They can change their algorithms, which will make you less visible. Or they can become irrelevant, and you'll need to move somewhere else. Or they can ban you.\\n\\nSocial media can be a powerful tool if you use it as an *additional* distribution channel to attract people to your *own platform*. This allows you to [go direct](https://mirror.xyz/safak.eth/KU5J8zVHQ7J13l3h_6sgmElfmMs5EF0E-cBXGQBskoM).\\n\\nA great benefit of social media is that you can connect with a global community of like-minded people. Use that to your advantage.\\n\\nA great downside of social media is that it can be taken away from you at any moment. Prepare for this.\\n\\nYou don't know what the algorithms are going to do in the future.\\n\\nYou don't know if the platform will survive.\\n\\nYou don't know when you can get blocked out of your account.\\n\\nWhen you own your distribution, you can be truly independent as a creator.\",\"timestamp\":1641218597,\"title\":\"Own Your Distribution\"},\"digest\":\"CxswFVdscGZSRadpCliHelo3Tk0_tzVZ-VRsEDM9s5Y\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x245305CEB1c3eDE978F9650286f0c411c4C45DCf\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"-RS2CmxQfmQtZ0eqIDlAUyyl685mKCGQ0nn2zAEBBkQ\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"cQRCUobfvDo28EZZDm3AX3fO8gyxAusDU4dztAyb4uY\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"E7iXYutLWGReHH_X1uaYflzpX6-PLpj7J3S81isdjrcCfEY7SkFA2HXVA8-mMfrn0NhRGT8qH_ChO-rjg2a-qg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x47800353dd8161b82cd66a23b92eaa03541c135a2e45759c9ef1756dc94a3f190d4f27a69de22ada9bd98a72b9ee88dab219d5476f974776ab929dbd19bc0d291c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"-RS2CmxQfmQtZ0eqIDlAUyyl685mKCGQ0nn2zAEBBkQ\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"cQRCUobfvDo28EZZDm3AX3fO8gyxAusDU4dztAyb4uY\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"83k1z1evxOIL9mBd5V-k2Xmy7WUD_WCNeb8w02E8eHY\"}"